summary: 2011 F-150 CONTINUES TO LEAK FROM REAR HEADLINER.  VEHICLE WAS BROUGHT INTO FORD IN 2013 AND 2014 FOR LEAKS.  FORD CLAIMED THE LEAK WAS COMING FROM THE THIRD BRAKE LAMP ON CAB.  VEHICLE CONTINUES TO LEAK CAUSING MOLDY SMELLING INSIDE ALSO MAKING VISUAL OBSTRUCTION INSIDE OF VEHICLE DUE TO MOISTURE BUILD UP.
